---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Diaspora Founder Guides: Honest Intelligence for Ghanaians Abroad"
  description="Practical guides for diaspora Ghanaians considering business or investment in Ghana. GIPC registration, fraud prevention, remote-viable models, and trust mechanisms. No hype."
  keywords="Ghana diaspora investment, diaspora business Ghana, GIPC registration guide, Ghana fraud prevention, remote business Ghana, diaspora founder Ghana"
>
  <div class="hero" style="padding-top:7rem;">
    <div class="hero-noise"></div>
    <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;">
      <span class="hero-tag">For Ghanaians Abroad</span>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,2.8rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:0.75rem;letter-spacing:-1px;">Diaspora <span class="gradient-text">Founder Guides</span></h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;">Honest, practical intelligence for Ghanaians abroad considering business or investment back home. We tell you what fails, what works, and what requires your physical presence.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
      <p>Diaspora guides are advancing through the v3.0 publishing pipeline. Each article passes 8 stages with 3 mandatory quality gates and includes 4-audience breakdowns.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card coming-soon reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="feature-card__icon">&#x1F4DD;</div>
        <h3>GIPC Registration: The Real Process</h3>
        <p>What the official website does not tell you. Timeline realities, capital requirements, common rejection reasons, and the documents you actually need.</p>
        <div class="card-meta"><span class="pipeline-badge">In Pipeline</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card coming-soon reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="feature-card__icon">&#x1F4BB;</div>
        <h3>Remote-Viable Businesses in Ghana</h3>
        <p>Which business models actually work with fewer than 4 visits per year. Cash control systems, local manager selection, and the models that survive distance.</p>
        <div class="card-meta"><span class="pipeline-badge">In Pipeline</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card coming-soon reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="feature-card__icon">&#x1F6E1;</div>
        <h3>Trust and Fraud Prevention</h3>
        <p>The fraud patterns that catch diaspora founders repeatedly. Land title scams, construction fraud, employee theft, and the control systems that actually work.</p>
        <div class="card-meta"><span class="pipeline-badge">In Pipeline</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
